Install through python exe.
Install pip through get_pip.py
python get-pip.py
python C:\Python27\Tools\Scripts\win_add2path.py - To add pip to path - pip works only if the command prompt is in admin mode.
install VCForpython27.msi
pip install pandas
pip install "ipython[notebook]"
pip install scipy - works on only those systems which have BLAS,LAPACK and ATLAS libraries(details
scipy installation details - http://www.scipy.org/scipylib/building/windows.html#blas-lapack-and-atlas
pip install pyparsing ## prerequisite for matplotlib
Install matplotlib from exe.
pip install -U scikit-learn
